@API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5212
@API_HTTPS = https://localhost:7291

### Health Check
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new booking
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "guestName": "John Doe",
  "guestEmail": "john.doe@example.com",
  "guestPhone": "+1234567890",
  "roomId": "ROOM-101",
  "checkInDate": "2026-02-01",
  "checkOutDate": "2026-02-05",
  "numberOfGuests": 2,
  "totalAmount": 500.00,
  "notes": "Late check-in requested"
}

###

### Get all bookings
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/bookings
Accept: application/json

###

### Get booking by ID (replace with actual ID from create response)
@bookingId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}
Accept: application/json

